<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>If you had to give this class a title to proclaim it's presence, it would have to be &quot;Masters of versatile damage&quot;.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Well with that said it was taken from a &quot;Prima&quot; guide so I guess it's not necesarily a SoE / Verant title.  But with how much of a hand SoE / Verant probably had in making the guide and definatly had in giving Prima the info my question is, are we now officialy the &quot;Masters of versatile damage&quot;?<br>
<br>
Heck if the shoe fits. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=artillis>Artillis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0> at: 5/21/03 4:25:42 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=delfontes>Delfontes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 138<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/21/03 4:34 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Masters of Versatile Damage?</span><hr size=1> Cold/Magic/Fire based nukes/lures.<br>
<br>
Sounds versatile to me. Though we do need a bigger cold nuke <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=qaman>Qaman</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 3209<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/21/03 4:53 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Masters of Versatile Damage?</span><hr size=1> &gt;&gt;If you had to give this class a title to proclaim it's presence, it would have to be &quot;Masters of versatile damage&quot;.<br>
